    <div class="comment-wrapper-main"><div class="comment-wrapper-main-inner">
			    
          
      <div class="content">
        <p>I have a question. I am really wanting to do a detox - but I have a great suspicion that I fall into the category of folks who can't do it. I have Bipolar Disorder. Not only am I on 10-12 different medicines every day, it has been drilled into me how important eating habits are to someone with Bipolar Disorder. But with so many meds, so many mood changes, do much stress, can't you see why I might WANT to detox ?! Is there anything I can do to do a partial detox that would still keep me eating full meals, but I might get something out of it? Or anything you may suggest?</p>
              </div>
    </div></div>
        
